    "en": {
      "title": "Tamil National Federation supports Dulles beauty queen",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Tamil National Federation has unanimously decided to support the presidential candidate Dalas Alagaperuma.",
        "TNA Media Spokesperson and Jaffna District Member of Parliament MA Sumanthran said this.",
        "He mentioned that 'Tamil Tessia Federation has unanimously decided to support Dulles Alagapuruma in the meeting held today.",
        "Meanwhile, it is noteworthy that the Leader of the Opposition Sajith Premadasa, Janatiphi candidate Dalus Alagaperuma and Professor G.L. Peiris participated in this discussion."
      ],
